WEBVTT

00:00.500 --> 00:14.500
Workspace Health is your system status dashboard. Navigate to Settings, then Workspace Health.

00:15.000 --> 00:29.000
Green means ready. Yellow means attention needed. Red means blocked.

00:30.000 --> 00:44.000
Click any red item for step-by-step resolution.

00:45.000 --> 00:59.000
Re-run the check to confirm all systems are green. A healthy workspace means reliable inspections and accurate reports.
